Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.43,Song,,0,0,5,,Nani mo nai tadatada tsudzuku sora
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.43,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Nothing is endless as the everlasting sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:19.46,Song,,0,0,5,,Nani hitotsu te ni todokanai yōna
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.43,0:00:19.46,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Nothing out there that is out of my reach
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:25.77,Song,,0,0,5,,Ano hi no biru no sukima kara mieta gaitō ni
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.46,0:00:25.77,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Tonight's streetlights in between buildings sites\NAre too bright on me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:29.21,Song,,0,0,5,,Watashi ga nanimonona no ka tte
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.77,0:00:29.21,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}For so long I \NDidn't know who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.98,Song,,0,0,5,,Utau koto wa nanina no katte
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.98,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}What songs I sing \NAnd what songs I sang
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:37.85,Song,,0,0,5,,Ano hito ha ai o kuretakatte shiritaku mo nai
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.98,0:00:37.85,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}For long enough that the one offering love \NDoesn't want to know me now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:43.86,Song,,0,0,5,,Demo itamunara kono itaminara
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.85,0:00:43.86,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}But even if you're getting hurt, \NEven if it hurts a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:50.33,Song,,0,0,5,,Mōsukoshi mōsukoshi itai gurai ga ī
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.86,0:00:50.33,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}In a little more, just a little more\NThis pain will turn to joy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:56.57,Song,,0,0,5,,Kirainara kirai to ima kotoba ni shite
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.33,0:00:56.57,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Say you hate me, say all you want\NYour words don't frighten me a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:01:02.37,Song,,0,0,5,,Mienai ashita o koko de owara sete
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.57,0:01:02.37,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Cause if you do, your tomorrow, \NUnseen before, will die for good
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:08.88,Song,,0,0,5,,Demo an'nani aishita kon'nani aishiteru
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.37,0:01:08.88,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}But how I loved you before,\NI love you now just as much
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:18.82,Song,,0,0,5,,{\fade(0,600)}Sono shiawase no hitotsude ī oboete ite
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.88,0:01:18.82,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2\fade(0,600)}And how sincerely happy we were in old days\NI will never forget
Comment: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:20.79,Song,,0,0,0,,{OP ED border}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:36.51,Song,,0,0,10,,{\fade(2000,0)\an8}Closed for stocktaking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right... \NYes, I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Those machines are more sophisticated than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.15,0:01:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was damn sure \Nthey are nothing but interior...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Riichi Eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:46.45,Song,,0,0,0,,*guaranteed bonus in next roll
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Has he been here for long?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.95,0:01:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... For longer than he should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You spend the whole morning loafing.\NIsn't it time to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:02:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong! I brought the manuscript to editor in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, not bad. \NBy the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,how come you're playing pachislot for hours now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just so that I could write \Na really comprehensive article.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But since when are you taking \Nsuch a keen interest in the article?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural. \NSince I now know about Sloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it about the sloth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I just meant to say \Nthat I'm a slow starter with unfamiliar topics...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't wanna editor to scold me any more \Nfor being superficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya is a {\i1}slow-starter?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure you're not trying to make an excuse \Nfor being easily distracted?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I wouldn't say I'm always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? \NEditor summons me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:51.02,Default,,0,0,10,,{\fade(600,0)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0.996\shad1.295\blur1.494\3c&H626259&\4c&H7A6F77&\b1\fnHitch Hike\fs44.813\fscx114\fscy92\4a&H2C&}Episode 2 \N {\fs85.642}God's Finger
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.28,0:02:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Declined?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned only general details, but no insides! \NNo specifics of the process!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}General details?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:03:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always taken up the cases with ardour before, \Nalthough you're not fond of publicism.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But until you learn to get to the essence,\Nthe dream of becoming a novelist will remain a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after rewriting the same article for a millionth time.\NPretty much what you're doing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll leave you to work.\NBeen a pleasure seeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya...\NAny idea why he bumped you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's complicated...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something that distracts you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't exactly call it distraction... \NPachislot just turned out to be kinda exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Explains your lack of success in Pachislot magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The machines' technical specifications are important,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.66,0:03:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but until you let the joy of the game embrace you, \Nyou're doomed. Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Narticles need more solidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not interested in the subject, \N neither is the reader.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If this goes on,\Nyou'll lose your employneck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up? \NAfter I've already put so much effort into it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Lose your employneck.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even go spin some drums!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri will be worrying and complaining \Nthat I slack off again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, I can't find this solidity \Nanywhere else but in Slothium.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I hoped to see noble warriors \Nfighting for the champion's title there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, having seen it myself,\NI can't be sure of anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya? Gin...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I always thought of pachislot \Nonly as of a blunt game for over-aged morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But that time... In Slothium, when I became a play member myself and got involved in the the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even notice how I got obsessed with pachislot. \NI forgot about everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time something had me \Nthat fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't you think you get carried away too easily?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Got carried away, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come the damn on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The manuscript was rejected?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:23.27,Song,,0,0,10,,{\an8}Open
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's okay, \Nboss rejects whatever he considers imperfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri is being too worried about one loafer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.54,0:05:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. \NYou sure he didn't reject it out of his bad mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Ginya recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, just now on my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he took my prank to heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense! Take offense at jokes and withdraw \Nis totally not like Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, time for you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri works part-time at a gym now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Striving to be a sports instructor, \Nshe always dreamt of becoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's practice in advance for Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, master, take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:05:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great? \NSeeing one fulfilling a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you speaking of that \Nas if you don't have a single dream yourself, Ishibashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure I do, at least one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Although now I'm an ordinary office clerk as well, \Nin fact, I would sincerely like to be a reporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:15.29,Song,,0,0,10,,"Gym" and "jimu" (office work) sound alike
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to write about what I see with my own eyes, \Ntell people about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm so worried about Ginya's article being rejected. Master, what's your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dream, you say? Once upon a time, I had a dream \Nthat I had the determination to never part with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,To support the youth's dreams - \Nall that's left for me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it seems to me, \Nyou're not telling the whole truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Something in this gloomy master's look betrays \Na dreamer in him, even though he won't let it surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My God, it's so late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you see Ginya,\Ntell him I stopped by to wish him luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I look like a dreamer \Nwho forbids himself to dream,{\i0} huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it... Maybe I just wasn't born Japanese \Nto understand them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried my best, \Nbut there's no use crying over spilt milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing tomorrow I rush to Slothium. \NOnly in the heat of the game, my luck can be fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,For I am a pachislot-reporter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to Slothium\Nfirst thing in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm running low on the advance payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The tournament schedule is drawn up by the authorities, \Nsuch are the rules. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Slothium prohibits training games.\NOnly actual matches are allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they better send me this schedule sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so impatient about getting there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishibashi came through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri is also worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I let you see Slothium \Njust so you could write a fine article.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect pachislot to infatuate you that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. \NI understand it all, but what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The game ignited me to the core before I could notice it. \NThis is beyond my will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing wrong?\NI'll never get it by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Morn...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, youthful one? Was one rejected manuscript enough to make you that gloomy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk nonsense! \NWhere do you see a hint of gloom on this face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your nail, it's broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! \NDisinfection is required!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No need, no need! \NI'll be fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! How can one be working as a writer \Nwith a wounded finger?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how small the wound is, \Nall of them should be tended to. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:54.85,Song,,0,0,10,,{\an8}Open
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I think I'll go...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Interviews, interviews!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Reckon he will be even more absent-minded now. \NAll he has on his mind is the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"There is one place called..." Oh damn, no good, no good. \NIt's not an article about Slothium only.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to invite you to lunch tomorrow. \NIn a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A restaurant...{\i0} \NFor real?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind to lunch with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't! \NI don't mind, not one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, at 1 pm in front of the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,At 1 pm in front of the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, please come sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what should I eat?\NA hamburger? No, a steak...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The restaurant oughta be the unusual one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:56.37,Song,,0,0,10,,{\an8}To Mr. Otonashi Ginya
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Members Tournament - Round Two."\NNo way! An invitation from Slothium!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. Begins on April 18th at 1 pm... \NAre you goddamn kidding me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how small the wound is, \Nall of them should be tended to. Right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, I feel so sorry for you.\NThere's no telling if he'll make the right choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:26.91,Song,,0,0,10,,{\an8}You will be more beautiful than love itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too, had to quit gymnastics once \Ndue to a minor injury...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:29.21,Song,,0,0,10,,{\fade(600,0)\an8}You will be more beautiful than love itself with Miake jewelry
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,To leave the athlete's path behind. \NGive up the desired fate and live a worldly life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The today game's rules are as following: \Ninitial score - 200 points. Final score - 2000 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The game starts in five seconds...\NFour seconds... Three... Two... One...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he interested in member's tournaments?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe in some of them in particular?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks at this rookie guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The game has just begun...\NI mustn't be hasty now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's taking him so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Will he actually come today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! \NRiichi Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But which one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.47,0:11:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.. \NHe's more collected than the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting hotter up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Unsheathing your favourite weapon? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The number you have dialed \Ncould not be reached...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now! \NGonna hit Big!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why has it stopped?\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? \NBlackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Otonashi's machine got unplugged?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are Slothium rules that strict on the participants?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?\NWhy was only my machine unplugged?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there no justice in Slothium whatsoever!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet, please. \NThe Game is still going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The accident that happened to Otonashi Ginya \Nhas induced a stop command.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But nothing has happened to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nothing...\NJust a scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Slotter's life is in his fingers. \NPlease follow me at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But... what about my game?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi's progress is suspended.\NYou will be scored with "No game."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You can replay the current match another day.\NNow, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Big!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the top now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:13:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise... Slothium's building is equipped \Nwith such an exclusive first-aid post...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In high-level games, the physical and mental state \Nof the participants is subjected to severe stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it's not a reason to make the full-arm X-ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,At times, even the marginal case can be life-threatening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Life-threatening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The bone is intact. Still, I suspend you from the game \Nfor two days. Take care now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Life-threatening high-level games...{\i0}\NWhat's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Otonashi,\NI hope your injury wasn't too serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What about high-level games, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.09,0:13:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of institution is this Slothium anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Having my nail slightly peeled off, \NI get an X-ray, and the game rescheduled!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The schedule will be rearranged for you. \NYou'll be notified. For today, you are free...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just tell me!\NWhat is my level?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Here and now! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want to know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the deal with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:14:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Only rogues sneak up on people \Nin that shinobi manner! What are you, a cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Daiba hasn't done anything to you.\NWhat are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You are... just a newcomer, \Nrecognized by Slothium as one of its members.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is... My passion for pachislot \Nwas first ignited here in Slothium.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I don't understand why. But that's why \NI came here today - hoping to find the answers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But as I feared, I flared up in excitement again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I realised it,\NI got carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wanted to see you, whose rank is superior!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, \NI wanted to play against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Until you grasp the local rules, our showdown is impossible. Consider this my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What you wanted to understand \Nis Slothium ranking system.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep in mind, the administration wants the system \Nto remain obscured from the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how to keep secrets, my man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent. \NIn that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:15:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordinary challengers recognized by Slothium \Ncomprise the foundation of the pyramid - the Members.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Members' count is 298...\NThis is my current rank, I reckon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, exceedingly successful members get promoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They are assigned the rank of Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, {\i1}skill plus manner,{\i0} followed by the special \Npersonal exam, get you the promotion to General.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, the one crowning the pyramid is King.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,King?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The best of the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, this man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the Ultimate King. After becoming a knight, \Nhe hasn't lost a single of his games.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He was destined to hold this title.\NKing of Kings. Daiba Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,With his power, one can even arrange matches \Non his own, irregular, rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was that man...\NThe Ultimate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really something! Can you believe it? There are \Nas many as 298 people like me, and I'm one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Slothium is, in fact, \Na considerable enterprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you not in the mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to talk sense into you, Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:16:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief.\NYou have your head stuffed with pachislot now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder, master!\NDo you happen to know Daiba Ryo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure I do!\NHe's the Ultimate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew all along he's not some layman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine how strong he is.\NNow I'm even more determined to meet him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.52,0:16:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it fun, playing pachislot?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That was quite fun for me though. \NWhile waiting for Ginya, I had some time to imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Women tend to dislike the guys \Nwho don't keep their promises. But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What I dislike even more is people forgoing the dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't hold any grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, my work is over for today. Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri... Wait! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You rarely see her so upset.\NDid you screw it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll surely... make amends somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I did my best, \Nbut Daiba Ryo's name is not mentioned anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What damn kind of person are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I both let Yuri down \Nand failed to make any progress with my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Slothium, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then! \NWhere else can I start my quest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know when to stop!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep bothering us,\Nyou will lose your membership and get kicked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! I just want to see Daiba Ryo, \Nwhat do you care about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the rules forbid me to play yet.\NDaiba, I only want to watch {\i1}you{\i0} do the play!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To see your game!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I have some time to spare.\NFollow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll settle it with the owner later. \NLet him go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? \NTrembling already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a special hall for General and above games.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,General and above?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The initial score is 300.\NGame will last for 5 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,For a rule-violator like you are, I can't spare more \Nthan five minutes. The choice of machine is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The limit is 5 minutes. Need to score as much as in a full-weight game. I was given a chance... I'll seize it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,First, gotta get a grasp on the machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:19:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! What's the deal with you? I still haven't won \Na single time! How's Daiba... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Daiba frozen in such a daze?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does he not move a bit? Is this the guy called the Ultimate King? He hasn't stopped a single drum yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait though, I got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,While I'm rushing headlong with full-weight bets, \Nthis guy is acting carefully, saving all the coins!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What Ultimate King are you then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba has finished only 3 games so far.\NKeeping this pace, he hopes to win by the score!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Two minutes left.\NI just need to hit one good Big!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Small Factor, Small Factor...\NNothing but Small Factors!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And this guy...\NHow is this guy doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on you'll see, \Nit's not about techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya, I believe, \NLady Luck has abandoned you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a single one of your drums \Nwill have seven on it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, \NI'm Luck's favourite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm driven by her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense! He barraged the buttons and hit Big... \NIs this what the Ultimate King's finger capable of?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Time's up. \NIf you excuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I leave,\Nwill tell you just one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If the slotter's heart depths are filthy, \Nhis game is also bound to be filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The reel is still spinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba... Ryo...
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.34,0:21:20.69,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}The heavy rain is over now, \NShadows have ceased to roam, \NEven summer itself has come to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:20.71,Song,,0,0,5,,Ame wa yande ita kage to aruide ita natsu ga owatte ita
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.69,0:21:34.27,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}My youth goes on, pushing me in my back with no rest,\NAnd the scarlet sky will soon start pouring water again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:34.29,Song,,0,0,5,,Seishun ga boku no senaka o oshite akai sora utsuru mizutamari
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.27,0:21:47.89,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}With my leg in a clutch, suddenly the sky shivered, \NSo unawares, making such stupid look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:47.89,Song,,0,0,5,,Ashimoto ga tora rete ite sora wa ureru bakaridatta
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.89,0:21:54.56,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So it will remain forever,\NAs I will remain forever so!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:54.56,Song,,0,0,5,,Konomama de īkai boku wa konomama de īkai
